               ♪♪

72
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:28,107
           [rumbling]

73
00:03:28,209 --> 00:03:29,475
        What is going on!?

74
00:03:29,899 --> 00:03:31,699
               ♪♪

75
00:03:31,878 --> 00:03:33,512
          Yaks destroy!

76
