            [grunts] [crashes]

92
00:04:13,354 --> 00:04:15,787
 Yak's head never been so clear.

93
00:04:15,911 --> 00:04:17,911
               ♪♪

94
00:04:18,058 --> 00:04:19,291
        This is AWESOME!

95
00:04:19,693 --> 00:04:20,993
             [shout]

96
00:04:21,517 --> 00:04:22,216
[bang] [bang]

97
00:04:23,017 --> 00:04:24,217
[bang] [bang] [bang] [bang]

98
